    Class and Description
    MultiIaaSJobDispatcher
    A simple trace processor that creates as many VMs in the cloud as many is required to host single jobs (e.g., if the job requires 1024 processors then it will create 16 VMs with 64 cores if the PM with the largest size in the cloud could host 64 core VMs).
